# UNRDF CLI

Command-line tools for RDF graph operations and ontology-driven code generation.

## Installation

```bash
npm install -g @unrdf/cli
```

## Quick Start

```bash
# Generate code from ontology
unrdf sync

# Validate RDF files
unrdf validate ontology.nt --summary

# Convert between RDF formats
unrdf convert schema.ttl schema.nt

# Query RDF with SPARQL
unrdf query "SELECT * WHERE { ?s a ?type }"
```

